<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12pt 0cm 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;">教师队伍作为职业教育发展的首要资源，其“双师型”教师培训不仅满足教师自我提升之需，且契合当前职业教育发展的迫切需求。为推进学校师资队伍建设，落实职业教育高质量发展，落实党中央、国务院相关指导意见，1月19日，我校有幸邀请董先明副教授为全体教职工主讲《“双师”教师认定培训》专题讲座，讲座由副校长徐江伟主持。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12pt 0cm 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12pt 0cm 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-01-22%2017%3A12%3A28%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%878.jpg?Expires=2021274748&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=H0t5sSeJhlp0qTgzyqbyC3e3QhA%3D" alt="" width="650" height="432" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12pt 0cm 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;">董教授首先从认定依据相关文件展开介绍，抛出问题，并以问题为导向，强调在职业教育领域中主动了解和研读相关政策的重要性。从“引”“育”“留”“评”四个方面解读文件要求与举措，同时强调要注重专业成长、能力提升，外部培训和内部辅导相辅相成，这样才能使教师在内外部的推动下更好地成长，实现自身与团队的共同提升。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-01-22%2017%3A12%3A48%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%873.jpg?Expires=2021274768&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=N20E7rlGX%2FF%2Fzv%2FVeumS8Q9E0QA%3D" alt="" width="650" height="432" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;">他在培训中强调，“双师型”教师个人成长应与“双师型”教学团队建设相结合，旨在构建一支品行优良、技艺精湛、专兼职相结合、富有活力的教师队伍。倡导学校参照国家制定的专业标准体系，规范化培养、引进人才，推动职业教育教师管理过程的科学化，全面提升“双师型”教师队伍的专业素养。并落实提质培优计划，深化职业教育改革，打造双师型教师队伍。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;">最后结合自己的工作经历，从国家职业资格证书制度、职业技能鉴定的流程和考评技术等十四个方面道出了他关于“双师型”教师的评定研究与实践思考。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-01-22%2017%3A13%3A06%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%875.jpg?Expires=2021274786&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=Zf3vlCkbTGLm%2FIrUFc5mpvOkIiY%3D" alt="" width="650" height="432" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;">徐江伟副校长在讲座结束时强调，“双师型”教师培训工作对学校发展的重要性，特别指出这是本科层次职业教育高校高质量发展的必由之路。她表示学校将一如既往地搭建教师发展平台，创造条件全力支持教师专业素养的提升。最后她对受训教职工表示通过本次培训要学以致用，将所学知识与技能更好地运用到教育教学工作之中，达到以学促教、以学促改的目标。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;">以学赋能，砥砺奋进，本次培训提升了我校教师理、实一体教学能力、专业实践技能等“双师”素质；思行并进，聚势赋能，为实现本科层次职业教育高校的高质量发展贡献力量。</span></p><p><br/></p>